description: This phospholipid biosynthesis shows a schematic overview of the major pathways for phospholipid biosynthesis in yeast. The mainphospholipid biosynthesis pathway included in this figure is;  phosphatidylcholine/phosphatidyl- ethanolamine (PC/PE) reacylation pathway. This figure shows the conversions and enzymatic reactions recquired for the PC/PE pathway.
title: Phospholipid biosynthesis
